import Vue from 'vue'
import Router from 'vue-router'
import HelloContainer from "./components/HelloWorld.vue"
import Exam01 from "./components/Exam01.vue"
import ExamMessageBox from "./components/ExamMessageBox.vue"
import ExamField from "./components/ExamField03.vue"
import Login from "./components/login.vue"
import login05 from "./components/MyField_taobao_05.vue"
import form from "./components/ExamForm06.vue"
import tab from "./components/ExamTab07.vue"
import tabbar from "./components/ExamTabbar.vue"
import F from "./components/weixin01/F.vue"
import Home from "./components/weixin/home.vue"
import messageList from "./components/weixin/common/messageList.vue"
import loginxz from "./components/xz/login.vue"
import product from "./components/xz/product.vue"
import homexz from "./components/xz/home.vue"
Vue.use(Router)

export default new Router({
  routes: [
    // {path:'/',component:HelloContainer},
    {path:'/exam01',component:Exam01},
    {path:'/ExamMessageBox',component:ExamMessageBox},
    {path:'/ExamField',component:ExamField},
    {path:"/login",component:Login},
    {path:'/login05',component:login05},
    {path:'/form',component:form},
    {path:'/tab',component:tab},
    {path:'/tabbar',component:tabbar},
    {path:'/f',component:F},
    {path:"/Home",component:Home},
    {path:"/messageList",component:messageList},
    {path:"/loginxz",component:loginxz},
    {path:"/product",component:product},
    {path:"/homexz",component:homexz},
    {path:"/",redirect:"/homexz"}

  ]
})
